Transform 2d css Property
-translate(x-axis , y-axis) , translatX() , translateY()
-scale(width , height) , scaleX(width) , scaleY(height)
-rotate(deg)
-skewX(x-axis) , skewY(y-axis) , skew(x-axis , y-axis)
-matrix(scaleX() , skewY() , skewX() , scaleY() , translateX() , translayY())

Transform 3d css Property
- prespective ==> (body , transform Tag)

Animation css Property
-@keyframes
-animation ==> animation-name , animation-duration , animation-iteration-count , animation-direction 
-animation-delay

